          "settings": {
            "text": "Timeless, graphic and casual, the striped sailor shirt is a state of mind, the cornerstone of the French art de vivre. Atelier Marinière has reinterpreted it in a slightly more oversized version. Designed to be worn on all occasions, from lazy evening hikes on the beach to a casual dinner at the restaurant, this mariniere is knitted in a breathable, mid-weight cotton yarn, perfect for any season.Only 99 pieces, numbered in the order they are sold. Made in Italy and hand-machined by our skilled knitter.",
