          "settings": {
            "heading": "Details",
            "icon": "none",
            "content": "<p>Atelier Marinière Volume 1.</p><p>Designed to be worn on all occasions, from lazy evening hikes on the beach to a casual dinner at the restaurant, this mariniere is knitted in a breathable, mid-weight cotton yarn, perfect for any season.</p><p>Only 99 pieces, numbered in the order they are sold. Completely made in Italy</p>",
